Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they're going to have jets that are faster than the supersonic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.50,0:00:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to bounce off the atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.82,0:00:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to thank you and Susan,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.46,0:00:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and I want to just state before everybody that I claim you as my teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.38,0:00:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The question I have has to do with constant prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.12,0:00:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I want to heal something around Christianity,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Christ, and my relationship to God that comes from my childhood,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.70,0:01:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but my father conditioned us with beliefs from a Christian sect
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.03,0:01:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that was based in revelations and apocalypse and an angry God.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.49,0:01:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I was attracted, after I became spiritual for the last 20 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.95,0:01:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I was more attracted to godless religions like Buddhism,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.15,0:01:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,where there wasn't as strong a concept of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.21,0:01:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But through your teachings over the last three years,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.67,0:01:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've realized,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.47,0:01:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen Christianity and God from a new perspective,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.21,0:01:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm grateful for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.39,0:01:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This summer, I've taken a three-month sabbatical to focus on constant prayer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and to spend time in the wilderness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.75,0:01:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,where I can focus on making it as much a part of my life as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.91,0:01:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The questions I have have to do with the prayer I'm choosing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.69,0:01:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I took your teachings that I had heard,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.37,0:01:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and I used the prayer,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.61,0:01:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Glory be to thee, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:01:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thy will be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And I repeated that over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.87,0:02:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,As time went on,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.71,0:02:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of my life came up before me,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and I started to see how much I needed salvation,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and what I felt as I wanted to switch to the Jesus prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Jesus prayer has the statement of,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.04,0:02:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,for Lord Jesus Christ,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,have mercy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.55,0:02:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,have mercy on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.41,0:02:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,a sinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And that didn't feel good to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.87,0:02:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,so I used the terminology,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.29,0:02:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Jesus Christ,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask your mercy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.73,0:02:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and I repeat that over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.36,0:02:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So the question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.64,0:02:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is that an appropriate language to address Christ in a prayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you aware of what you call the Brother Lawrence,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the practice of the presence of God by Brother Lawrence?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be a good thing to look up,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's really sort of what you're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, it's a very small little booklet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know where you can get any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.22,0:03:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the prayer of Brother Lawrence, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.96,0:03:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, to be constantly conscious and aware of the presence of God,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.46,0:03:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's boiled down to its probably most simple form,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, what should we call it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the word I want?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.14,0:03:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we call it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.14,0:03:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.14,0:03:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The practice of the presence of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.48,0:03:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.48,0:03:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The practice of the presence of God by Brother Lawrence is very famous,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.48,0:03:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,time-honored, and has been used for great periods of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.48,0:03:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I mean, if you're looking for something that has been validated by widespread usage,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.48,0:03:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.48,0:03:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.86,0:03:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The practice of the presence of God is the name of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.86,0:04:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The last question I have about the prayer is that,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.86,0:04:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,as I'm walking down the aisle,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.86,0:04:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.86,0:04:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,walking in the wilderness,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,it starts to take a singing quality,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,kind of like a choir singing the prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And maybe because of my childhood and my scrupulosity around Christianity is,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want that to be a disrespect of the prayer,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.86,0:04:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but it seems to happen naturally and it also feels good as I'm praying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.86,0:04:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's the angelic response.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.12,0:04:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.12,0:04:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's primarily singing in my consciousness and very little just.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.12,0:04:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the angelic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.12,0:04:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.44,0:04:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I was doing, was worrying about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be nice not to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the angelic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:04:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd like to have a picture with my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.99,0:05:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Angelic, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My question's also about prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Glory be to Thee, O Lord, Thy will be done,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,or the Jesus prayer,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,would it enhance it by having some sort of gratitude towards God,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,thanking Him or His divinity?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.43,0:05:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Being specific about gratitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I think we're too much interested in the words verbatim.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.36,0:05:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the overall intention of devotion can be expressed anyway, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.55,0:06:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I think any kind of wording that's comfortable to you, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.05,0:06:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the energy with which it resonates.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,so how the wording I don't think makes that much difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.12,0:06:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.71,0:06:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easier to write.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.51,0:06:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.83,0:06:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.83,0:06:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.56,0:06:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise I get all my weight on my elbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.56,0:06:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been doing the Course in Miracles workbook this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm finding at certain lessons, like for example,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I want the peace of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.95,0:06:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That day, it's like all hell breaks loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.95,0:06:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I feel guilty and I don't know how to work through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.87,0:06:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you should know what it could have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Flattened by a truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:07:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, don't forget, karmic propensities come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know, we expect that it's going to be the way we want it to be
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.56,0:07:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,by praying and asking for a miracle,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.56,0:07:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that your phone bill is going to be paid now and not shut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.79,0:07:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And we think, well, if they shut off my phone, it didn't answer my prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.31,0:07:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,God wants you to know if you don't pay your phone bill,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,they're going to shut it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You got the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called pay attention to reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.67,0:07:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't know whether you're getting an answer to the prayer or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.04,0:07:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And to puzzle out the meaning of what you experience next until you understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.80,0:07:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:08:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.24,0:08:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Tuesday night when I was meditating, suddenly the words came up,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,ask Dr. Hawkins how you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So and instantly total and complete terror came up to the point where I was almost physically ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.24,0:08:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's sensible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.24,0:08:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So in order to work through the fear, I came up and I'm asking, how am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.29,0:08:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing wonderfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.29,0:08:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.29,0:08:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,To get out in front of the audience when you're suffering from anxiety and overcome it, face it, and break it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What more could you ask for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.74,0:08:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.74,0:08:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.74,0:08:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:09:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.22,0:09:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.48,0:09:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,For the longest time, I've had a problem in terms of a personal connection to divinity, to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And I even wrote a book, Struggling to Surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.83,0:09:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave you a copy when I first met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.83,0:09:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just recently got it watching a 2002 video about surrendering
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to thee, O Lord of God imminent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.08,0:09:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.08,0:09:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you explain a little bit more about the connection between, is that like the gateway to God transcendent?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about God transcendent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.94,0:09:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The sky's fine the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You worry about, don't worry anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.13,0:09:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not really worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.13,0:09:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,God imminent is identical to what the world considers to be transcendent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.13,0:10:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But you see, a lot of people call God you, and it's an other, other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't realize that, you know, as Christ said, heaven is within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Heaven is within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Discover the infinite presence within oneself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.44,0:10:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,God is simultaneously transcendent and imminent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.86,0:10:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And those are merely artifacts of languaging.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Transcendent and imminent are not contradictory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just different ways of stylizing it and vocabulary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But traditional religion, you know, speaks of God transcendent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But Jesus said God is, heaven is within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.88,0:10:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,God is both transcendent and imminent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.01,0:10:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It was such an incredible gift to be able to see that, well, I'm not surrendering to something out there, but this bigger piece within myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's not an out there-ness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:11:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I don't like the term you for God.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.46,0:11:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a pronoun, you know, and it's limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.46,0:11:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't such a thing as you God.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.93,0:11:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The closest you can come is to thee, O Lord, to thee, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.93,0:11:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thee is respectful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.93,0:11:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And thee implies the recognition of the divinity because that's the only thee that appears, you know, historically.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.80,0:11:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,To thee, O Lord, is God transcendent, spoken of respectfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.47,0:11:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.47,0:11:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You say you, O God, you're making it like two persons, two personalities separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There's me and then there's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's sort of a not too evolved kind of comprehension of divinity, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.20,0:12:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's what 95% of the world gets transcended down to or, you know, what was my understanding of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.70,0:12:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The ineffable is very hard to put into words.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,About seven years ago, I was involved in a group of a spiritual teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.80,0:12:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I had...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.80,0:12:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Involved in what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.04,0:12:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've got...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Does she have to be closer or further?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've got real dramatic changes in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.56,0:12:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But about five years ago, I moved away and I lost any contact with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.56,0:12:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to continue my study with the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.59,0:13:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But right now, the group, for an outsider like me, looks much more like a sect than the group that it used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Same group.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.91,0:13:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just you see it differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.91,0:13:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.91,0:13:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I just see the teacher and the group itself differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.91,0:13:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more like a splinter group, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.91,0:13:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.91,0:13:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, their attitude to the teacher and her role in the world and their role of religion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.03,0:13:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And in her teaching and so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like they're creating a new religion with her being a messiah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The leader of this group.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.28,0:13:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The leader of this group.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.37,0:13:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A new messiah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.37,0:13:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.08,0:13:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to redo the calendar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Make this year one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just wanted to ask you to calibrate the information coming from her back then and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:13:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:13:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want any names.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.12,0:14:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You hold in mind the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.12,0:14:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher is over 200, is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,240?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.83,0:14:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,500?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.83,0:14:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,600?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,505?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,510?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.50,0:14:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,505?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A lovingness, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So basically, I can continue doing the studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I can continue doing the studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.94,0:14:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.94,0:14:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She can go through all that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.94,0:14:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Her enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.94,0:14:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Her enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Her enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.94,0:14:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Her enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Her enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.01,0:14:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Her enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.01,0:14:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Her enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But my energy is remaining high.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.27,0:14:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's .
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They're cultizing around her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The other people in the group are cultizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.36,0:14:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They're cultizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.80,0:14:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.80,0:14:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't go in the details of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.60,0:15:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher feels all right at 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.92,0:15:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.92,0:15:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody ask me another question if you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.04,0:15:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.04,0:15:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.56,0:15:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to ask a question, and I also want to put it in a context, so that the question
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.56,0:15:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So that the question becomes clearer. My question is if being
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.98,0:15:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Being and feeling grateful
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.57,0:15:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,allows
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,For grace to flow down. Yes onto one gratitude gratitude
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.70,0:15:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The context is I have a business to run a business to run
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.92,0:15:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah business, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.22,0:16:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Noticed that whenever I think of promoting my business
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Marketing anything of the sort nothing works
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.42,0:16:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as I start working on myself by addressing by working by reading a book like this by
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.18,0:16:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Listening a tape that you have as long as I step away from business and concentrate on developing my conscious
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah consciousness and you attract then everything works. Yeah. Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.98,0:16:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm true, however, I still have a business to so I'm still attached
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.77,0:16:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A little bit. So what I'm trying to do is I'm trying to ask people for testimonials
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.21,0:16:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,When they get help through my business
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.07,0:16:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,However, that doesn't happen
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.87,0:16:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm trying to see within myself
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.04,0:16:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is something that I need to undo or get better with on my own so that it happens
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.18,0:17:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning am I not grateful enough myself that they don't feel grateful to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.87,0:17:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you ask them for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.31,0:17:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, them for a testimonial. Yeah, if they have what's a relief of suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.96,0:17:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the result you feel better. Could you give us just the result of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a refrigerator. What is it? I'm a doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, and so they come to me because they have pain and so I help them with it. Are you looking for testimonials?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I wouldn't know as illicit them would not even bother
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.14,0:17:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,because
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,because
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,what what furthers your
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.90,0:17:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Practice is
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.80,0:17:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Word of mouth. Yeah, that's that's personally where my
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,feeling is yes
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:18:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I wouldn't ask them for testimonials because things would really happen on their own if I'm getting yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.86,0:18:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's what I'm thinking too
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it happens spontaneously, right? Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.84,0:18:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much. I know from experience. Yeah, mm-hmm
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.10,0:18:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you do all that you can to the best of your ability
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And the energy of that radiates out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.26,0:18:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And then other people hear of it, and they send somebody,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and they do the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And then your practice grows and grows.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.15,0:18:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And you have to run away to Arizona.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Out in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiding in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.86,0:18:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.66,0:18:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to look into the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.42,0:18:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a real camera, so look into the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.62,0:18:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.30,0:18:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange things happen on this planet, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:19:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm reporting back that strangeness predominates.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.68,0:19:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.70,0:19:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.74,0:19:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, I want to say thank you with all my heart and soul
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,for your teachings and for your devotion to your students.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.36,0:19:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.13,0:19:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have a question about the student-teacher energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There seems to be a field of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.09,0:19:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,a consciousness that I sense between you and all of us as your students.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.71,0:19:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And at times, it arises within me an awareness of your presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.81,0:19:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And sometimes it arises as the hearing of the Kyrie music spontaneously just arises within me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:20:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And I sense that you in us, your presence is with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.67,0:20:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And I would just like you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.83,0:20:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe comment on that phenomena and your sense of your accessibility to all of us in this plane and when you are around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.45,0:20:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I pray every night to be a servant of everyone here, to be a servant of God, to be a servant of these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.15,0:20:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And I give gratitude, I thank God for the gift to be able to be what I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.82,0:20:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I am to the students, you know, that to me is a great gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.12,0:20:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And as I told you, my obligation is to God, my fellow man and myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.61,0:20:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And my fellow man is that as a teacher, just as I was the best physician I could be, to the fullest extent I could be that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.80,0:20:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the best hermit I could be to the degree I could be a hermit for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.20,0:21:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And now I am back in the world in this particular function.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.45,0:21:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But I do hold all of them in mind and pray for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And I pray for the spiritual evolution of everyone here present because they are indeed my blessing and their gift, God's gift to me to be able to serve them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.60,0:21:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.60,0:21:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So you may be picking up the energy of the prayer itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.31,0:21:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel that I hear your voice in my head at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.31,0:21:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be the way the prayer is going to cross to you, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And I feel that that will be with me for all my days and beyond.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.88,0:21:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.17,0:21:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It is so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.49,0:21:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.49,0:21:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And thank God for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.56,0:21:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Blessing me by that, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.56,0:21:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.56,0:21:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You make a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.97,0:21:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my honor to know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.97,0:22:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.97,0:22:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.40,0:22:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.72,0:22:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She picks up the energy of the prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.52,0:22:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Something I heard you say in a recent interview that really stood out to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.11,0:22:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If I heard you correctly, you said that we have to master the world before we can transcend it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.33,0:22:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just wondered what you meant by that, because I think maybe I've been trying to transcend it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.25,0:22:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you have mastered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.64,0:22:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You see its value, and its value.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.28,0:22:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,To master the world really is to see its value.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.28,0:23:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,As a teaching tool, having learned all you can from the world, there's no further need for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.80,0:23:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a big toy, a big whirling toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.15,0:23:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.21,0:23:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fun toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.21,0:23:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It serves its purpose for a period, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.54,0:23:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we go on to other dimensions, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.54,0:23:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not the ultimate dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.54,0:23:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We go on to other dimensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.12,0:23:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.12,0:23:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt like I had started to understand the whole idea of karmic unity.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.14,0:23:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And the notion of the every hair on your head being counted, isn't that the same thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.62,0:23:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Same thing as what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.32,0:24:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what karmic unity means.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.02,0:24:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What does karmic unity mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.02,0:24:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the idea that everything leaves a karmic trace, and then, I don't know, you float in the ocean according to your karma?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.21,0:24:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, everything leaves, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.21,0:24:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything leaves a trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.21,0:24:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.21,0:24:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Renewable forever, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.21,0:24:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's my understanding of karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.21,0:24:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.21,0:24:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything that exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.21,0:24:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So then the idea of the hair on the head is also...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.21,0:24:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything exists, everything that ever happens leaves a permanent track for all time, for eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.63,0:24:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, you really don't want to make too bad of a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.63,0:24:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Because people are going to be reading it centuries from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.63,0:24:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll say, oh, that one there, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.63,0:24:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at what she did, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.63,0:24:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.63,0:24:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So then I pray for mercy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.63,0:24:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It leaves a permanent track.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.63,0:24:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.63,0:24:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's the same idea, just a different wording then.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.63,0:24:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.63,0:24:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.63,0:25:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything that exists emits an energy, including all events, personages, decisions, options.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.66,0:25:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And that leaves a karmic pattern, a track.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.72,0:25:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's what we call about our inherited karmic propensities.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.92,0:25:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.92,0:25:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.43,0:25:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.36,0:25:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going as fast as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.43,0:25:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My Widow Wicks can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.43,0:25:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going as fast as my Widow Wicks can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.04,0:25:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been suffering from depression for like 15 years or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.67,0:25:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.67,0:25:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm trying to search for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.67,0:26:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't think the cause is like, I don't believe it's like sugar, like you just say
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.67,0:26:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,before.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.67,0:26:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She's suffering from depression.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.67,0:26:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.70,0:26:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She has been for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.80,0:26:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.85,0:26:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've been treating with a doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.85,0:26:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,With what?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.85,0:26:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been treating with a doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.85,0:26:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.85,0:26:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I am an antidepressant right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.85,0:26:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.85,0:26:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.85,0:26:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Antidepressants.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.85,0:26:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She's on antidepressants.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.85,0:26:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.85,0:26:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it helping?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.85,0:26:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.01,0:26:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.01,0:26:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But I would like to, like, get a deeper healing or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.40,0:26:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.40,0:26:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.40,0:26:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.40,0:26:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.40,0:26:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So the wisdom to accept that which you cannot change.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.74,0:26:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The wisdom to change the things you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.74,0:26:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The wisdom to know the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.74,0:26:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So you do all you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.74,0:26:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're responsible for the effort but not the result.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.74,0:26:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And many of these depressive things come and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.74,0:26:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And you stopped eating sugar and sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.74,0:26:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you try that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.74,0:26:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.74,0:26:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.06,0:26:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.06,0:26:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've tried the antidepressants.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.06,0:26:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.06,0:26:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.06,0:26:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.06,0:26:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.06,0:26:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.06,0:26:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.16,0:26:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.16,0:26:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.16,0:26:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.27,0:26:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.27,0:26:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.27,0:27:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.27,0:27:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.27,0:27:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.27,0:27:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've tried the easy ones like functional hypoglycemia and all those kind of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.46,0:27:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you may have to just wait it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.46,0:27:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So these depressions tend to run their course.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.60,0:27:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You may run 10, 15 years and then disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.60,0:27:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So you just maintain whatever level you need to keep the dopamine, to keep the serotonin
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.60,0:27:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,level up in the brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.60,0:27:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's genetic generally.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.79,0:27:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And you do what you can during the period of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.85,0:27:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,When that's necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.85,0:27:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, you add to it all you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.85,0:27:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.85,0:27:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been doing a course in miracles and all of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.85,0:27:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You do everything else you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.85,0:27:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.48,0:27:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Using alternate health.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.48,0:27:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything from acupuncture to who knows what will help.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.48,0:27:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All those things are worth a trial run.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.48,0:27:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.48,0:27:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You never know which one is going to be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.48,0:27:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.58,0:27:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been trying acupuncture and lots of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.58,0:27:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're doing what you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.58,0:27:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.58,0:27:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.58,0:27:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.58,0:27:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.12,0:27:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.12,0:27:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.12,0:27:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.12,0:27:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.12,0:28:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.12,0:28:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.12,0:28:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.12,0:28:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.12,0:28:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.12,0:28:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.12,0:28:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.31,0:28:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.88,0:28:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.88,0:28:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.88,0:28:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're doing what you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.20,0:28:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better than being in denial.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.61,0:28:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better to face it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.99,0:28:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do what you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.13,0:28:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than be in denial.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.61,0:28:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And then some other solution will appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.77,0:28:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.80,0:28:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Take more vitamin B3.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.80,0:28:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut out sugar and sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.80,0:28:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Try acupuncture.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.80,0:28:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Try jogging.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.80,0:28:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,God knows what will help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.24,0:28:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.24,0:28:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.85,0:28:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.85,0:28:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I have suffered from headaches for about a year and a half.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.85,0:28:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Headaches?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.81,0:28:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.41,0:28:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I have epilepsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.94,0:28:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.56,0:28:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Epilepsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.84,0:28:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.34,0:29:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've been to a neurologist, and the second one has made the headaches a bit better.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.72,0:29:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of every day, they're probably about five days a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.28,0:29:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.72,0:29:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've read that you suffered with migraine headaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.18,0:29:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.78,0:29:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was curious on what you did to pass that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.53,0:29:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I did everything under the sun, including acupuncture.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.45,0:29:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Acupuncture helped everything, but it didn't cure the migraine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.89,0:29:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had pins and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.21,0:29:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I did the whole thing, moxie combustion, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.95,0:29:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It had cured my ulcer, you know, first treatment or second treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.47,0:29:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't do anything for my migraine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.39,0:29:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,See, but I think everyone is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.26,0:29:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Imitrex came along, and it was like magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.76,0:29:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I took a half an Imitrex, and like magic, it disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.72,0:29:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.96,0:29:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, they have me on Zomeg.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.56,0:29:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.98,0:29:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a nose spray that I take when I feel the headache coming on.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.13,0:30:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I also have what they call chronic headaches that are not considered migraines.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.33,0:30:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Cluster headaches, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.63,0:30:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so you have to, everything's physical, mental, and spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.23,0:30:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So you handle it on all three levels, and then you wait it out,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.89,0:30:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and a lot of these things you'll grow out of.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.73,0:30:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.19,0:30:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.73,0:30:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you just told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.49,0:30:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of the things I had when I was young were all gone, bye-bye, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.19,0:30:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't get them until I was older.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.63,0:30:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what's so bizarre.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.91,0:30:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.15,0:30:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.51,0:30:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't get any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.79,0:30:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.99,0:30:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.47,0:30:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.77,0:30:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't old enough to get them yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.17,0:30:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And my own personal experience, middle age was the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.21,0:30:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't one thing after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.79,0:30:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it was a wonder I survived at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.79,0:30:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you pass the migraines, or do you still get them?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.23,0:30:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The migraines still will recur periodically if the weather's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.63,0:30:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So weather can affect migraines.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.05,0:30:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If the weather comes on, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.37,0:30:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I live in Texas, so I've heard that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.49,0:30:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So right now, I'm not eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.89,0:30:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm eating chocolate, because you can see it's sucking in.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.34,0:30:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to kind of put anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.92,0:31:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So you say, well, that's a belief system, and you can negate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.28,0:31:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've been negating it, but I don't want to push my luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.98,0:31:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've heard that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.50,0:31:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,When the barometric pressure is dropping, it's not a great time to indulge in chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.04,0:31:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've heard that acupuncture has healed some people of epilepsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.34,0:31:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Has what?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.28,0:31:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Healed people.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.12,0:31:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.70,0:31:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of wonderful things can be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.26,0:31:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, there's different acupuncturists with greater and lesser skills, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.34,0:31:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,like any other physician.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.70,0:31:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know which one's good and which one's bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.56,0:31:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you just work on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.90,0:31:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You try your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.98,0:31:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You go by reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.36,0:31:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You use kinesiology if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.20,0:31:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.64,0:31:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, this doctor has capacity to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.36,0:31:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.44,0:31:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.42,0:31:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.38,0:31:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so lovely to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.92,0:31:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.66,0:31:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Human beings are fragile.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.60,0:31:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a wonder how we stay alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.78,0:31:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I just marvel that we've survived it all, frankly.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.24,0:31:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When you think of all the afflictions that can hit you in one lifetime,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.00,0:32:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that you know about, and the ones that you didn't know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.65,0:32:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.98,0:32:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The other day, we're rounding a bend, and Susan's driving,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.04,0:32:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and we're out in the country, a sharp turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.62,0:32:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and coming right at us at a breakneck speed, right in our lane,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.35,0:32:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,is a guy just dying to have a head-on, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.98,0:32:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you know, totally unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.94,0:32:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Minding your own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.38,0:32:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Went to church that morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.84,0:32:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on the bed, and here's a maniac coming right at you, dead on,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.08,0:32:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,right in your lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.64,0:32:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Right in your lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.04,0:32:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,God knows what.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.49,0:32:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Very scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.07,0:32:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have time to be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.37,0:32:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It was over before I got a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.41,0:32:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy 80th year.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.05,0:32:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.71,0:32:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My question, is the enlightenment level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.62,0:33:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the level where there's no thinking, thoughtlessness, no mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.34,0:33:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and is it also the level at which you're released
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.42,0:33:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,from personal karma?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.14,0:33:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to answer about personal karma,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.76,0:33:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,because there's karma at different levels,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.12,0:33:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and different consequences on different levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.28,0:33:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can go beyond the karma of this level,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.72,0:33:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're still stuck with the karmic propensities of humanness,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.88,0:33:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and et cetera, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.58,0:33:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the first question?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.48,0:33:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is enlightenment the same as the level at which the thinking ceases?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.40,0:33:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.80,0:33:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind becomes silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.92,0:33:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There is instead, in the high 500s,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.62,0:33:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,an exquisite joyfulness, an ecstasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.38,0:34:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There then comes a bliss and an infinite state of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.74,0:34:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The peace of God, it's unmistakable.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.38,0:34:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You realize when you go into it, you recognize the peace of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.47,0:34:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Timeless, infinite.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.48,0:34:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And without thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.46,0:34:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember any thought, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.34,0:34:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You also can, this is in Sikpat 600,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.30,0:34:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you can also leave the world at that point,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.78,0:34:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're aware that you could leave if you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.26,0:34:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nobody to wish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.94,0:34:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So I suppose there's more karmic propensities than anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.54,0:34:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,whether one will continue to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.50,0:34:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is a strong desire to leave the world at that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.18,0:34:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.77,0:34:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an option, with the door standing open, invitationally.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.12,0:35:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why, oh, I forget, probably the majority of people at 600 leave, do.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.29,0:35:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why there's hardly anybody beyond 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.77,0:35:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Most people leave at 600 or more, a higher level.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.04,0:35:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Each level, you have an option to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.48,0:35:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And sometimes you don't know what's going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.94,0:35:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You wait and see if you're going to leave or not leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.68,0:35:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.20,0:35:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.54,0:35:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.66,0:35:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to see you, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.60,0:35:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.94,0:35:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a state of infinite peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.16,0:35:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.59,0:35:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.55,0:35:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is about wolves in sheep's clothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.36,0:35:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,as you've been talking about today.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.50,0:35:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.02,0:35:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.97,0:36:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're ever disguised as a spiritual aspirant,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.27,0:36:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and if it's ever okay to deal with people under 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.15,0:36:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,when you feel like,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.05,0:36:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,oh, there's a spiritual aspirant,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.49,0:36:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,they could be wearing the sheep's clothing of a spiritual aspirant,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.73,0:36:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,is that what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.49,0:36:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.97,0:36:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But inside they're really demonic and evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.79,0:36:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm sure of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.11,0:36:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.51,0:36:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.95,0:36:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it, you always warn, stay away from under 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.03,0:36:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away from under 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.71,0:36:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I think to avoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.39,0:36:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Avoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.81,0:36:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus Christ said don't oppose evil, avoid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.34,0:36:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had a lot of interesting people come into my life lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.52,0:36:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have made exceptions because I didn't know how to say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.00,0:36:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.72,0:36:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't know how,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.38,0:37:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,it feels unloving and unkind to say no when somebody is in desperation,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.34,0:37:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet it's such a drain.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.94,0:37:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a test.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.70,0:37:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to know how to be able to say no without feeling guilty about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.36,0:37:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a test along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.14,0:37:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I said yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.39,0:37:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That was just negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.85,0:37:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That was very negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.83,0:37:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And what I said to the people who were in the room,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.12,0:37:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was 법lless in my own life,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.04,0:37:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I said to the people,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.74,0:37:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I said God, God, a question that I've been asked in my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.41,0:37:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,a question that I've been asked in my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.67,0:37:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,just to be able to think that God and I are close,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.71,0:37:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that we're not the same,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.57,0:37:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that we're not the same,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.37,0:37:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,we don't have a common purpose,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.65,0:37:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,help, help, help.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.66,0:37:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think the most important thing that I can say is,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.76,0:37:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I think people will try to cling to you and hang on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.54,0:37:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like the crabs in a pail,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.74,0:37:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the crabs in the pail,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.74,0:37:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,when one tries to get out and starts to go over the tide of the pail,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.02,0:37:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the other crabs pull them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.23,0:37:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have to know when you have to walk on,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.11,0:37:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,relationship with God, what do you want with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.87,0:37:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.69,0:38:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You can intuitively detect that they really
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.97,0:38:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,mean to pull you down with them in a parasitic dependency,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.74,0:38:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,which they juice you for your energies.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.87,0:38:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, they used to be called electric and magnetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.95,0:38:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a psychic lady in town that was pretty smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.45,0:38:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She would call them electric and magnetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.20,0:38:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The electric would give you energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.38,0:38:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and the magnetic would like pull your energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.20,0:38:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And she divided people into those that pull your energy
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.86,0:38:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and those that give you energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.22,0:38:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,People below your own consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.38,0:38:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,will be pulling energy from you, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.35,0:38:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in a pickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.12,0:38:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So you try to avoid them.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.93,0:38:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You can, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.75,0:38:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I agonized over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.31,0:38:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I shouldn't, and I agonized, agonized over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.43,0:38:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.31,0:39:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I could not say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.09,0:39:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know what you mean, yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.00,0:39:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,God knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.16,0:39:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in an extra bedroom, and can't you just
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.78,0:39:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,let me board here for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.34,0:39:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you discover they're doing evil incantations over your bed
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.48,0:39:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,while you're sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.55,0:39:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.41,0:39:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.05,0:39:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I understand what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.52,0:39:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of people run into that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.76,0:39:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a tough one.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.89,0:39:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why people go to Al-Anon, you know, because, yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.50,0:39:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why people go to Al-Anon.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.48,0:39:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you had any advice on how
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.78,0:39:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to practice this identification.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.04,0:39:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How to practice this identification with the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.28,0:39:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and unconditional love toward the self simultaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.06,0:39:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's the following all the things
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.28,0:39:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that we're teaching combined.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.67,0:39:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's following all the things combined, all of it at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.39,0:40:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And what was the first question?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.12,0:40:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How to practice this identifying with the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.62,0:40:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.18,0:40:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,To be aware that the functioning of the mind is not the real self.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.38,0:40:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind wants everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.94,0:40:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It wants amusement.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.24,0:40:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It wants to be bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.38,0:40:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's self-glorifying, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.14,0:40:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And you disown that as your own reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.48,0:40:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And you say that's the way the ego is.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.49,0:40:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And disown that you're identifying with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.86,0:40:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You can say, I am what I am despite that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.56,0:40:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite that, not because of that, or not that I am that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.35,0:40:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.94,0:40:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the animal nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.22,0:40:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You can call it animal nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.34,0:40:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Animal nature is greedy, desirous, narcissistic, vain,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.98,0:41:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,wants to control, wants to take over the territory,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.74,0:41:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,wants all the opposite sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.01,0:41:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.61,0:41:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stay compassionate at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.92,0:41:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But you recognize it's the animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.43,0:41:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Those kind of instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.51,0:41:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It always has to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.67,0:41:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to control.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.57,0:41:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It plays king of the hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.94,0:41:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Picture two wolf males, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.42,0:41:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm my territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.68,0:41:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm my women.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.62,0:41:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.42,0:41:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My women.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.48,0:41:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the USA and America.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.20,0:41:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the international situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.46,0:41:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's a part of me which isn't that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.42,0:41:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.85,0:41:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's bored with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.41,0:41:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Best to just be bored with all that,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.47,0:41:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,other than to denounce it as evil or bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.95,0:41:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's tedious.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.90,0:41:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's chasing your own tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.50,0:41:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Because no matter how much you gain,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.04,0:41:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,there's still more that can be gained.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.52,0:41:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're worth $100 million, you could be worth $100 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.94,0:42:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,could be worth $150 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.68,0:42:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're worth $150 million, you could be worth a billion.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.96,0:42:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're worth a billion, you could be worth $100 billion.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.50,0:42:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You could be richer than the Queen of England, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.44,0:42:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What good will it do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.94,0:42:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only eat one sandwich at a time,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.87,0:42:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,sleep in one bed at a time, drive one car at a time,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.24,0:42:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,make love with one person at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.38,0:42:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So it doesn't do you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.44,0:42:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,All the excess doesn't do much good.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.49,0:42:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,100 pounds of potatoes is better than one pound.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.87,0:42:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How many can you eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.93,0:42:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little nervous, so you have to excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.09,0:42:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have a question that's come to mind many times when I've come before.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.31,0:42:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And one of your wonderful teachings to include not being spiritually naive
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.77,0:43:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,is a big important lesson for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.78,0:43:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.28,0:43:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She's either too close or too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.04,0:43:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.88,0:43:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A big question for me is about the spiritual naivete
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.02,0:43:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and how important that was for me to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.68,0:43:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a big one for me, all these years of spiritual work.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.96,0:43:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the analogies.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.66,0:43:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the analogies you gave about Chamberlain versus Hitler
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.68,0:43:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and how Chamberlain went to Hitler and peace in our time.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.42,0:43:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And then that was a couple of times ago you gave us that analogy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.42,0:43:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the white paper, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.60,0:43:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.20,0:43:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I wonder how one stays integrous in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.90,0:43:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,in your life and your everyday comings and goings.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.06,0:43:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to work with folks that have calibrations that are not integrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.96,0:43:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So can you give some clues of how one
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.66,0:43:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,goes about the world and is able to make good choices
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.77,0:43:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and not change your own level of integrity to deal in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.13,0:44:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you try to choose the most integrous pathway you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.07,0:44:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you find yourself in a non-integrous one,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.25,0:44:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you try to find the most diplomatic way
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.21,0:44:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,to remove yourself and to stop identifying with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.13,0:44:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And hold in mind what you do want.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.17,0:44:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold in mind what you do want.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.38,0:44:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Because what you hold in mind tends to manifest.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.10,0:44:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So you hold in mind that which you would be pleased and desirous of.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.10,0:44:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You hold in mind what you do want and just refuse that which you don't want or leave
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.87,0:44:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.87,0:44:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You can say, I've worn it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.87,0:44:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.37,0:44:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.20,0:44:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You can say, I've worn it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.20,0:44:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.94,0:44:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Explored it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.94,0:44:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You've worn it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.61,0:44:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.61,0:44:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.16,0:44:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,May I have a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.16,0:44:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.16,0:44:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.28,0:44:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They keep him busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.28,0:44:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He's like the official photographer.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.82,0:44:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.82,0:44:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.93,0:45:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.93,0:45:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.93,0:45:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins and Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.76,0:45:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I have studied the Course in Miracles, and I'm working on it the second time.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.72,0:45:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And I work as a nurse practitioner.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.44,0:45:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.44,0:45:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And how do I incorporate my new change of view of the world and people into this
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.28,0:45:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,medical world?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.28,0:45:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.76,0:45:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You see it the way you see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.50,0:45:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And some of it rubs off, and some of it does not.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.52,0:45:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.55,0:45:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people you can even recommend they try doing the course.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.45,0:45:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you've seen a lot of people recover from a lot of illnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.49,0:45:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be careful about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.03,0:45:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't consider you some kind of a proselyte or nut, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.59,0:45:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.23,0:45:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So you just utilize it within yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.64,0:45:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and the patients benefit from the fact that you yourself are coming from a higher place, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.97,0:46:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been starting my day with the prayer from the course that I am here because of he who sent me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.07,0:46:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's been helping me as a guidance system that what I say or what comes out of me isn't just my opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.39,0:46:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.83,0:46:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's been helping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.99,0:46:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you do the lesson for the day, and you go about your business,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.31,0:46:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and you choose to be as loving, you know, instead of forgiving,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.89,0:46:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,if you choose to be as loving as possible, one way of being loving is to choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.65,0:46:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see forgivingness as an option, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.09,0:46:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.25,0:46:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.03,0:46:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If people could be better, they would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.29,0:46:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.87,0:46:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.29,0:46:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.79,0:46:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they're stuck where they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.99,0:46:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what Jesus said.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.05,0:46:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive them and they know not what they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.15,0:46:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.07,0:46:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.57,0:46:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.23,0:46:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You can forgive them.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.69,0:46:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to give them the keys to your new car, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.50,0:47:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm moving as fast as I can move.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.06,0:47:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.60,0:47:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.04,0:47:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister and I are from Seattle, and we're not going to ask any questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.38,0:47:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the most quoted person in our life, I tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.60,0:47:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we quote you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.30,0:47:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we quote you correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.24,0:47:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.54,0:47:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.02,0:47:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll lose all of our friends after a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.62,0:47:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll get...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.34,0:47:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just want to thank you so much for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.08,0:47:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for thanking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.26,0:47:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing that we've done is we have you on all the time through the night, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.30,0:47:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,so that whenever we wake up, you know, we hear a little bit and can go back to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.66,0:47:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.68,0:47:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.70,0:47:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people do for the music, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.65,0:47:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They like the music, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.59,0:47:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.35,0:47:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I do hope that I'm not just brainwashing myself all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.73,0:47:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I understand what you're trying to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.09,0:47:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And have some of my own thoughts, because we have you on all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.71,0:47:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You just want...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.43,0:48:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, what you want is that energy is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.73,0:48:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.89,0:48:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What you want is the energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.41,0:48:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.95,0:48:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.01,0:48:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.91,0:48:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So I just wanted to get your picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.39,0:48:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We all do that with certain kinds of music or incense or reminders, symbols, statues.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.91,0:48:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I could get up as easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.35,0:48:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot the octopus.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.48,0:48:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.79,0:48:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.48,0:48:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.34,0:48:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to ask you to om, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.08,0:49:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.14,0:49:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She said something.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.20,0:49:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.11,0:49:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.53,0:49:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.72,0:49:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.50,0:49:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I have lots of questions for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.58,0:49:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was wondering if I could spend the next hour with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.03,0:49:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.39,0:49:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You can.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.03,0:49:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.59,0:50:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.59,0:50:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.70,0:50:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your feet up here and put your bottom there.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.96,0:50:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Whisper in my ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.04,0:50:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.84,0:50:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.72,0:50:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.82,0:50:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want maybe some validation over some doubt I'm having in exploring sort of the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.36,0:50:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,inner realms of my psyche in a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.76,0:50:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been training in hypnosis, hypnotherapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.92,0:50:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And have been working with regression and going back to different seeming episodes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.72,0:50:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's like part of me that's doubtful.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.06,0:50:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Like there's sort of the witness that's looking over the occurrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.38,0:50:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what do you take yourself back to?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.20,0:50:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Something you specify in advance?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.08,0:50:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's with intention and like the cause of something occurring in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.66,0:50:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what is that connected with, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.36,0:50:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.66,0:50:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this connected with?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.82,0:51:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.16,0:51:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sort of a sense of something coming about, but there's some doubt in.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.70,0:51:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have to be literally factual.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.42,0:51:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.08,0:51:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.18,0:51:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.68,0:51:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be more that it recontextualizes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.68,0:51:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Significance, meaning, and all that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.96,0:51:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.44,0:51:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The specifics are not necessary, usually.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.72,0:51:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You see the symbolism of what was and what is now, and you see the connecting thread.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.17,0:51:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.01,0:51:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.50,0:51:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In certain types of past life recall, you're not remembering an event like you're watching a movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.72,0:51:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.22,0:51:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens is the actual event begins to rerun all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.72,0:51:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.72,0:51:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, witnessing or watching something like out there from here, you're in the movie,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.06,0:52:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and the movie is happening again with the same sense of reality as it did originally.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.08,0:52:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.40,0:52:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.65,0:52:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.19,0:52:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So the experience that.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.63,0:52:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was recalling was that I was sort of enslaved by this man, and that I had died,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.69,0:52:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,but instead of returning to maybe the light or, you know, I decided to sort of invade him in a way,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.09,0:52:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,like attach to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.51,0:52:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.69,0:52:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that seem like.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.75,0:52:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a possibility, or.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.23,0:52:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's a possibility, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.23,0:52:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.83,0:52:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.69,0:52:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.47,0:52:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.97,0:52:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.74,0:52:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.84,0:52:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do all these come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.59,0:52:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.03,0:52:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.09,0:52:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.63,0:52:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.69,0:52:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.17,0:52:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.11,0:52:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, we've come up to ask for a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.77,0:52:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.11,0:52:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.26,0:53:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Rob and I, um, have committed our relationship to be in service to each other on our path
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.48,0:53:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.36,0:53:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.80,0:53:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And we would love for you to bless that alignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.86,0:53:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can bless, what, your love, your unitedness, and your devotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.70,0:53:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That you do it for yourself, for the other, and for God, and for mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.08,0:53:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.36,0:53:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.42,0:53:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.90,0:53:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I said you'd do that for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.16,0:53:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.18,0:53:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.90,0:53:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.48,0:53:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.62,0:54:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.24,0:54:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing I'd like to express gratitude for your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.66,0:54:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.96,0:54:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And bringing people closer to God, and so much specific explanations on how to get over
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.56,0:54:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,so many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.80,0:54:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But my question is, I have so many health issues, and I'm wondering, is there a mindset
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.98,0:54:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to certain specific health issues, or a way to get over, to be healed from them?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.60,0:54:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we're going to put out a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.66,0:54:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.02,0:54:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.24,0:54:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.60,0:54:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I did a bunch of lectures years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.83,0:54:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Things I understood, things I treated, things that I myself experienced, and the answers
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.27,0:54:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,that I found, you know, for whatever good it might be, people have similar things.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.66,0:54:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really amazing the number of things you can go through in a lifetime and still survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.12,0:54:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, as you're, you know, when you put them all end to end, and write them all up,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.54,0:54:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,it's really quite awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.74,0:54:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.24,0:54:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, between blood clots, and lupus, and migraines, and all this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.82,0:54:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you get all that negative?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.02,0:54:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, where do you get all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.50,0:54:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Negative karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.50,0:54:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.50,0:55:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, because of the speed and the height of your own spiritual evolution, you bring
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.42,0:55:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,all these things up in one lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.42,0:55:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So how do you get over?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.42,0:55:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You go from here to there.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.42,0:55:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You pull in everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.42,0:55:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.42,0:55:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Every karmic whirlwind along the way, and you can slow that down by just being dumb
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.38,0:55:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and not trying to evolve spiritually.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.82,0:55:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Just zoning out.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.82,0:55:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.82,0:55:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.46,0:55:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.46,0:55:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.46,0:55:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.46,0:55:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.08,0:55:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.08,0:55:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.08,0:55:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.08,0:55:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.47,0:55:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back to thievery, or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.18,0:55:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're stationary.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.85,0:55:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Lon, from the San Francisco Bay Area.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.85,0:55:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.85,0:55:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,One question.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.85,0:55:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.56,0:55:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,As I promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.56,0:55:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,First, you stated in your writings that one can reach the 500 levels in this lifetime,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.56,0:55:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,in one lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.56,0:56:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.56,0:56:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Does one have to transcend from the low 400s all the way up to the 499s?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.56,0:56:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not a linear progression.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.18,0:56:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You can jump from 350 right to 510.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.18,0:56:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No stopping off in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.37,0:56:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm making a very serious surrender and seeing things at some great depth.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.37,0:56:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Some spiritual passion comes up, and you can jump 150 points in a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.03,0:56:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.34,0:56:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.22,0:56:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Presently, I'm a teacher at an urban middle school, public school.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.22,0:56:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.22,0:56:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wanted to identify the critical factor to be able to teach the best I can teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.84,0:57:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,To teach what?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.84,0:57:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.84,0:57:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.12,0:57:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The critical factor?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.12,0:57:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.12,0:57:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your willingness to be of service.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.12,0:57:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the student feels your love for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.41,0:57:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you love them, they'll do anything for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.41,0:57:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids will do anything if you express that love to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.73,0:57:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Not avert.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.73,0:57:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't say, kid, I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.73,0:57:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll think you're a pedophile.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.73,0:57:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.14,0:57:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a mentor.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.14,0:57:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a professor at the teacher's college who lived across the street from my grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.76,0:57:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And he became a great friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.12,0:57:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was into entomology, and I had some great specimens.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.12,0:57:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We swapped specimens.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.40,0:57:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But that camaraderie between me as a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.40,0:57:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I was about 10 or 11 at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.40,0:57:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And he was a full professor in the Department of Science at the teacher's college.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.56,0:57:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But that lasted me a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.17,0:57:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And in later years, his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.17,0:58:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who then became an internist.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.17,0:58:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He and myself became friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.17,0:58:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we've been friends forever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.27,0:58:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the value of some teacher in your life who allows you to experience the value of who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.12,0:58:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say the gift of being myself to the fullest extent I can to this child.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.36,0:58:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And let him know I appreciate his ambition and his interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.93,0:58:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.93,0:58:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.93,0:58:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Returning interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.11,0:58:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.11,0:58:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Atwood would say, boy, that's some specimen you got there.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.11,0:58:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, my pride would just swell up, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.30,0:58:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Luna moth about this big, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.30,0:58:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Took me all night in the swamp to get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.16,0:58:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All night long in the swamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.46,0:59:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.16,0:59:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know if it's for the highest good to move to Sedona.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.77,0:59:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.77,0:59:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't just say that like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.77,0:59:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be a decision you make.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.93,0:59:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.03,0:59:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to answer that for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.03,0:59:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I can answer that for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.49,0:59:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to come to Sedona for?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.58,0:59:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,To be around the energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.58,0:59:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,To be around what?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.58,0:59:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.38,0:59:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,For your own spiritual advancement.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.38,0:59:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, like holy.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.38,0:59:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean for your own spiritual advancement?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.38,0:59:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Like holy company?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.18,0:59:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So therefore, what is your question?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.34,0:59:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a ?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.76,0:59:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.76,0:59:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.76,0:59:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,To choose move for because of holy company.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.76,0:59:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.76,0:59:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What could be higher than that?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.76,0:59:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.81,0:59:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.81,0:59:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a great motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.81,0:59:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why many people came to Sedona.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.81,1:00:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They knew there was a certain spiritual energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.25,1:00:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the ooh, la, la, new agey.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.25,1:00:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But the actual.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.25,1:00:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Because even those who are misled are trapped in the glamour of all that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.54,1:00:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a core of reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.54,1:00:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a core of reality that they really do want spiritual advancement.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.80,1:00:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And I always try to tell them, try and avoid the amusements along the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.02,1:00:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to save time, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.02,1:00:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.40,1:00:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.16,1:00:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A great many people came to Sedona for that very reason.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.89,1:00:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of some spiritual pathways, some spiritual teacher, because of spiritual friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.89,1:00:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.59,1:00:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.48,1:01:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How does one best surrender or transcend joy?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.48,1:01:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Joy?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.41,1:01:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Joy?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.41,1:01:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Joy?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.99,1:01:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender or transcend joy?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.03,1:01:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.03,1:01:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,In the back of the mind, there is, depending on your own spiritual trajectory.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.28,1:01:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,In this mind, as exquisite as it was, was the knowingness that this too has to be laid down to the old Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.52,1:01:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That came as a knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.44,1:01:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This too must be laid down to the old Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.44,1:01:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And the state, it was the state that Ramakrishna also experienced.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.80,1:01:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It was exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.80,1:01:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the same state.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.80,1:01:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And I saw that one could get attached to that state.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.44,1:02:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Attached to the being in a state of high joy.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.79,1:02:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And in fact, it was more than high joy.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.79,1:02:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It was ecstasy.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.79,1:02:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ecstasy.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.62,1:02:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Timeless ecstasy.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.62,1:02:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And in this particular case, there was the knowingness that this too must be laid down,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.00,1:02:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,given, surrendered to the old Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.08,1:02:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And sometimes, like, the more I push it away, the stronger it gets.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.08,1:02:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't push it away.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.27,1:02:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.81,1:02:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say to push it away.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.81,1:02:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.81,1:02:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I said become.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.81,1:02:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Become that joy.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.81,1:02:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Become that ecstasy.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.10,1:02:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And know that sooner or later, one will need to go beyond even that.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.61,1:02:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.48,1:02:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't push it away.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.48,1:02:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't resist it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.51,1:02:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Become it to the fullest extent.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.51,1:02:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When I dance for you, I dance out of ecstasy and joy.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.33,1:03:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't repel it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.33,1:03:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't refuse it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.33,1:03:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's exquisite.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.33,1:03:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.02,1:03:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.02,1:03:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It does itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.02,1:03:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't require any person to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.53,1:03:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's automatically doing it itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.53,1:03:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Facing the patterns in the air.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.53,1:03:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And becoming out of joy and ecstasy, the essence of that pattern.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.53,1:03:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.53,1:03:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.53,1:03:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.53,1:03:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.56,1:03:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This question comes from Kansas, from my daughter and son-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.56,1:03:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.56,1:03:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.56,1:03:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.56,1:03:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.56,1:03:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.56,1:03:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.58,1:03:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.58,1:03:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.58,1:03:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.01,1:03:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.16,1:03:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.25,1:03:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.25,1:03:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.25,1:03:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.25,1:03:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.92,1:03:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.92,1:03:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.92,1:03:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.92,1:03:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.92,1:03:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.92,1:03:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.92,1:03:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.92,1:04:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.46,1:04:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.52,1:04:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't answer this, resist. No, I can't answer it. If it were me, I'd go for it, but I mean, you know, what more do you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.70,1:04:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's enough of an answer for them to go for it. They'll go for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.40,1:04:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Alaska is so incredibly beautiful, but you have to value the rural and the remote.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.72,1:04:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And they do.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.32,1:04:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.84,1:04:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.38,1:04:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. They are aware of those limitations.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.64,1:04:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's a great place to be.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.31,1:04:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.24,1:04:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You learn how to fly.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.13,1:04:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I think bush planes all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.43,1:04:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. There's no roads.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.26,1:05:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.34,1:05:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.50,1:05:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing this spontaneously for the first time without writing this out.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.50,1:05:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had a lot of deeply held beliefs that I was unaware of from the unconscious that have been profoundly affecting my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.14,1:05:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And those are surfacing.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.98,1:05:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And a lot of those are from my experience with my biological father.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.94,1:05:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,With your biological father?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.90,1:05:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,With my biological father projected onto God.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.94,1:05:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.48,1:05:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I surrender those?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.46,1:05:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, do you know which ones they are specifically?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.82,1:05:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Unforgiving.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.34,1:05:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Unforgiving, uh-huh. Judgmental, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.20,1:05:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Abandoning.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.30,1:05:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Abandoning.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.08,1:05:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.80,1:05:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Rejecting.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.72,1:06:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't see God as a hero.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.34,1:06:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Rejecting.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.40,1:06:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Rejecting.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.42,1:06:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Rejecting.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.44,1:06:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Rejecting.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.46,1:06:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, God is not androgenic, so don't identify divinity as masculinity, because that which
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.08,1:06:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,is beyond gender, that which is the source of the universe is also beyond all gender
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.40,1:06:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,or is not going to be this way or that way, so in a way you're talking about anthropomorphic
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.40,1:06:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,depictions of God, cast in a paternalistic view, and that's my criticism of old time
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.78,1:06:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,religion and the Bible and all, is seeing God as some kind of an anthropomorphic projection,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.85,1:06:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,so a temper, subject to jealousy and fits and punishing and all this kind of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.23,1:06:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't even realize this, Dr. Williams.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.55,1:07:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think that's too advanced in understanding of God, that's a very primitive
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.13,1:07:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.47,1:07:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.91,1:07:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a tribal culture on the other side of the world, thousands of years B.C., and
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.76,1:07:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the concepts were appropriate for the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.48,1:07:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I like the concept of divinity of the American Indian native culture, much more benign, much
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.08,1:07:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,more also feminine, to be the source of the spirit of all of life and its expression as
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.48,1:07:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,nature and divinity and the animal forms.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.10,1:07:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the spirit guides, the spirit guides to the various animal forms are a reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.74,1:07:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, there are spirit guides for each one, yeah, there are spirit guides for each
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.57,1:07:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,one.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.57,1:07:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there's a condensation of spiritual energy of that animal's nature, and we wrote
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.14,1:08:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,about it in Power Versus Force, I think, energy fields, so what this animal knows is a radiation
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.20,1:08:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,of the knowingness of that field.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.16,1:08:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.55,1:08:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.55,1:08:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So when it leaves the physical body, its spirit goes to the one spirit, because the animals
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.71,1:08:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,all have one spirit, and that's the god of the leopard, or the god of the monkeys, or
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.78,1:08:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,the gods, so these various gods, which is typical in Hinduism, those are energy power
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.62,1:08:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,fields, attractor fields.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.98,1:08:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The word I'm on is attractor field.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.28,1:08:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.28,1:08:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the collective attractor field of that animal species, and it makes sense to,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.16,1:08:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,again, the pantheon of gods of Hinduism makes sense, because there are energy constellations,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.28,1:08:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you see, which represent that animal knowingness, that animal way of beingness, and that type
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.26,1:08:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,of animal grace, you see?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.62,1:09:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Each animal has its own grace, even though it may look terrible to you, that is its grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.44,1:09:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.44,1:09:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Better to eat you, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.60,1:09:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.60,1:09:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.60,1:09:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.60,1:09:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.60,1:09:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So Native American and Hindu pantheons, you know, get the energy field of the, the attractor
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.46,1:09:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,energy field of those life forms, and they are valid.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.80,1:09:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They are valid.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.80,1:09:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.79,1:09:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you don't want to get them mad.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.92,1:09:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.92,1:09:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll work harder.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.59,1:09:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.59,1:09:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.59,1:09:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.59,1:10:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.04,1:10:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.04,1:10:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had any thing to say, or any particular advice for me as a young gay man on the spiritual
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.02,1:10:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,pathway.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.02,1:10:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.22,1:10:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems very complicated.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.76,1:10:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it does.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.76,1:10:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And the politicalization of today's world, and the legalities, I grew up to consider
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.49,1:10:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,platonic love a valid.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.36,1:10:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Intense, sometimes far more intense than heterosexual love.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.22,1:10:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And some degree of it is innate to being in the service, where the bonding, and the loyalty,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.34,1:10:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and the love of the men for each other can be very, very powerful and very strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.38,1:10:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And I consider that legitimate.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.37,1:11:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether one gets into sexualization brings up a whole new thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.37,1:11:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The seven deadly sins, one of them is lust.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.37,1:11:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.37,1:11:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,To surrender the lust aspect, you know, to supplement the lust aspect, try to make it
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.98,1:11:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,more of a Hellenic classic, the love between men was celebrated in those days.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.72,1:11:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Celebrated.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.97,1:11:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.97,1:11:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Platonic love.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.97,1:11:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So, platonic love is an ideal.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.97,1:11:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ideal.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.97,1:11:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.04,1:11:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it were my own condition, I would strive for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.04,1:11:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.04,1:11:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And I would also use this as maybe an opportunity to transcend something that other men are really
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.07,1:11:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,stuck in, and that is lust itself, or its own sake.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.07,1:11:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you could look at it as an opportunity to let go.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.58,1:12:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the way you transcend lust, or any desire, you'll find that every desire, whether this
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.58,1:12:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,is for alcohol, for drugs, for sexuality, comes up first as an image in the mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.58,1:12:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.96,1:12:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't first get the thing, you first have an image, and if you're quick enough,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.96,1:12:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll see it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.96,1:12:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, no, I don't get an image of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.96,1:12:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought of a drink, it just was in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.96,1:12:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it was the thought of a drink.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.96,1:12:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens is the thought of a desire comes up first.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.96,1:12:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you can eliminate that thought the instant it's there.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.96,1:12:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you allow it to linger, it will draw more and more energy, and finally, it will reach
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.96,1:12:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,a point where you cannot say no to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.90,1:12:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the secret of how to overcome any addiction.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.90,1:12:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.90,1:12:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What I see happen with some people, gay people, is they get addicted to sexuality and carnality
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.90,1:12:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,for its own sake.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.93,1:12:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The downside, then, is to get sucked into sensory pleasure and carnality.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.22,1:13:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The upside is the opportunity to transcend that and deny that, and that's the Hellenic
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.22,1:13:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,tradition, where the sports figures were the great figures of the time, and where the love
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.44,1:13:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,of one man for another was traditional.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.86,1:13:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way I'd hold it, in my own understanding and my own development of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.86,1:13:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Read some Plato.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.99,1:13:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Read some Plato.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.99,1:13:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.99,1:13:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Read some Plato.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.99,1:13:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.49,1:13:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Platonic love means non-sensual, non-you call indulgent of the senses, non-whatever.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.32,1:13:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you call it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.31,1:13:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You can eat for survival, or you can eat out of gluttony.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.31,1:13:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So I see sometimes gay couples fall into what I would call sensual gluttony in the experiential
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.31,1:13:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,framing of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.31,1:14:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And some I've known for many years, and they're, you know, the same as an ordinary married
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.88,1:14:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,couple of any kind.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.88,1:14:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Helpful, helpful teammates, loyal, and forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.49,1:14:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.49,1:14:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.04,1:14:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.20,1:14:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.24,1:14:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.24,1:14:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.24,1:14:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I'm here, I know a lot less than I used to.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.84,1:14:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.84,1:14:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I know a lot less than I did before I moved here.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.57,1:14:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I seem to be reacting to everything in my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.21,1:14:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I have my little mental commentaries going on.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.57,1:14:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I react emotionally to everything, and I can't tell.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.69,1:14:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I look at things, I can't tell what's real, and what's just the way I'm interpreting it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.57,1:14:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just need a little help getting it in context, because I'm just nothing but reactions
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.57,1:14:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,lately.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.70,1:14:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Emotionally reacting to everything?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.70,1:14:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.70,1:14:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.70,1:14:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So how do you become detached?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.70,1:15:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you emotionalize everything?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.70,1:15:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.70,1:15:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.62,1:15:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.62,1:15:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's just a habit.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.62,1:15:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just look at a dead mouse on the floor and say, oh, it's a dead mouse.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.13,1:15:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender the theatrics and the drama.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.13,1:15:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop being a drama queen.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.44,1:15:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.44,1:15:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to dramatize everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.44,1:15:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.60,1:15:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.60,1:15:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to experience a thing and see what it is, you don't have to dramatize it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.60,1:15:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes people get to thinking that, oh, it's a dead mouse.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.63,1:15:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.63,1:15:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.63,1:15:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.63,1:15:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.63,1:15:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.63,1:15:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.63,1:15:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.63,1:15:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.63,1:15:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.63,1:15:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.63,1:15:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.63,1:15:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.63,1:15:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.63,1:15:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be thinking that that's their duty as a woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.63,1:15:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to dramatize.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.63,1:15:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.63,1:15:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You can be detached and cool and cold and say, that's a mouse, so what?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.63,1:15:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.63,1:15:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll pick them up.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.63,1:15:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.63,1:15:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to scream and faint and fall on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.63,1:15:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not all about me, probably.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.43,1:15:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.43,1:15:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything that happens is probably not all about me.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.43,1:15:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.43,1:15:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.43,1:16:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you're really complaining about is sort of excessive emotionalizing.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.43,1:16:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.43,1:16:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So I pray to God to help you transcend emotionalizing.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.87,1:16:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Pray to become more detached.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.46,1:16:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Intellectualize it and mentalize it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.76,1:16:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.74,1:16:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Emotionalizing it is coming up through the solar plexus.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.84,1:16:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mentalizing it is bringing it up to the head.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.49,1:16:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So try to bypass the solar plexus and put it in the form of thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.93,1:16:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.51,1:16:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think about it, not what do you feel about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.79,1:16:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.11,1:16:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The world doesn't care what you feel about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.85,1:16:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.03,1:16:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I've noticed.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.01,1:16:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They really don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.91,1:16:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You like this?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.70,1:16:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody says, yeah, that's well.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.66,1:16:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, I don't like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.76,1:16:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.51,1:16:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now try doing, force the energy up, you know, from the solar plexus up into the mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.21,1:16:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The thinkingness chakra.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.79,1:16:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.91,1:16:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The thinking.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.22,1:17:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,To mentalize about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.06,1:17:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.50,1:17:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Write a little mental thing about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.14,1:17:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.72,1:17:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a practice.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.92,1:17:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just habit.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.87,1:17:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.69,1:17:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And it follows family traditions, cultural traditions, and you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.97,1:17:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.40,1:17:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Cultural styles.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.76,1:17:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Men don't have that problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.77,1:17:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The plan is, don't you have any feelings?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.79,1:17:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's what I was thinking about, Henrietta.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.63,1:17:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.99,1:17:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten days ago when I came here, I got direction from you that I haven't been able to get in four years for the treatment of the lower astral attacks on my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.63,1:17:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.15,1:17:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wanted you to tell me about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.57,1:17:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wanted to thank you, Andrea, Dr. Kallenbach, and Susan, for the support.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.15,1:17:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I found a psychiatrist.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.77,1:17:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going this next week in Texas to see him.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.43,1:18:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The astral attacks have been very hard.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.31,1:18:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a biochemistry, it's a problem in brain chemistry and biochemical.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.89,1:18:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very easy to fix.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.02,1:18:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very easy to fix.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.40,1:18:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I watched her go into an attack on Friday, and for the very first time, she started to say, no, I rebuke you, and I refute you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.58,1:18:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And all she could get out was no, and she got stuck into the state.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.38,1:18:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What would have lasted five minutes only lasted a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.36,1:18:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.88,1:18:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.62,1:18:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And all she kept saying was no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.82,1:18:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But in her mind, she was thinking, I rebuke you, and I refuse you in the name of Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.04,1:18:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So she wanted to come meet this man that finally believed her that she's not crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.14,1:18:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.48,1:18:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You refute it, and you also biochemically block it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.38,1:18:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.06,1:18:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Because anything wrong in the nervous system, the entity will use that.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.56,1:18:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.34,1:18:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Like unconsciousness, brain injury, drunkenness, those, that's the, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.21,1:19:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's like the human becomes vulnerable then.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.17,1:19:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So you offset it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.67,1:19:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So pharmacology, you're doing all the right things.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.63,1:19:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.17,1:19:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.81,1:19:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She wanted to say thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.07,1:19:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing all the right things.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.85,1:19:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.53,1:19:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,May we get a photo?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.07,1:19:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be better.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.81,1:19:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.43,1:19:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,These things can be awful when they happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.71,1:19:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But also, very often, you can find the solution, and the solution is often very simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.35,1:19:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you can turn on a lot of these things.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.01,1:19:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A half a milligram a day of prolixin can turn it on and turn it off.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.77,1:19:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.13,1:19:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Something simple like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.46,1:19:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.34,1:19:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All on the scissor, that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.60,1:19:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.94,1:19:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Grab a photo, dear.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.12,1:19:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.44,1:19:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You can perforate an ulcer and take one tablet of something rather than the ulcer cures.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.54,1:19:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.66,1:19:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.84,1:19:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is physical, mental, and spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.18,1:19:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So you take care of all three at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.37,1:19:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is physical, mental, and spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.69,1:20:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You hit it on all three levels.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.03,1:20:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.04,1:20:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get any negative feeling around here.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.22,1:20:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She's going to be better.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.38,1:20:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Harkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.18,1:20:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.82,1:20:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you hold my hands while I ask this question?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.56,1:20:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.08,1:20:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.59,1:20:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Often when I meditate, I'm beginning to become deeply relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.87,1:20:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,My neck will go backwards like this as I relax, or it'll go to the side and contort like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.51,1:20:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wondering if it's safe for me to let it do that, because that happens at the same time that,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.19,1:20:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, the meditative state is deepening.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.45,1:20:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it safe for me to do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.28,1:20:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can refuse it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.28,1:20:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.57,1:20:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But what happens is when I change my body back to being upright, I lose the progress
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.01,1:20:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that I had made the previous, like, four or five weeks.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.63,1:20:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, try breathing it up to a higher chakra.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.43,1:21:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep breathing it up to the crown chakra, the energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.11,1:21:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep breathing the energy up to the crown chakra.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.72,1:21:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand how to do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.96,1:21:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You breathe.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.96,1:21:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You picture the energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.96,1:21:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the energy stuck when you're having this problem?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.62,1:21:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand how to do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.62,1:21:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the energy stuck when you're having this problem?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.25,1:21:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're afraid to stop what?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.25,1:21:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My body from going, like, so my neck will go backwards like this, because I've heard
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.80,1:21:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that people go into psychotic states sometimes when their neck goes back like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.40,1:21:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wondering whether it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.86,1:21:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that not so?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.86,1:21:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.86,1:21:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.63,1:21:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.09,1:21:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sometimes, and it's often, like, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.44,1:21:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.44,1:21:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.44,1:21:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you want to do is when you feel that in there, picture it going up.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.83,1:22:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Picture it going up.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.77,1:22:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.51,1:22:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,To your brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.51,1:22:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.51,1:22:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,To the crown chakra.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.51,1:22:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.51,1:22:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't concentrate on fixing the physical.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.51,1:22:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Concentrate on the breathing.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.80,1:22:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it'll fix itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.80,1:22:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll fix itself, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.20,1:22:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.20,1:22:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.54,1:22:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.54,1:22:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.54,1:22:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.54,1:22:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.54,1:22:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,May I touch your feet in gratitude?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.54,1:22:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.54,1:22:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.54,1:22:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And would you please touch my head again?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.45,1:22:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And what?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.45,1:22:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Touch your head.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.45,1:22:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you wish.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.45,1:22:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.64,1:22:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.52,1:22:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It serves.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.35,1:22:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.35,1:22:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.35,1:22:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.02,1:22:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.02,1:22:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.02,1:22:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.02,1:22:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.02,1:22:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.02,1:23:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.44,1:23:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.44,1:23:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.44,1:23:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is for you to be a servant, My встречe Servante, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.44,1:23:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I give thanks for your divine devotion, your love for God, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.92,1:23:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.60,1:23:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a tradition from India.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.00,1:23:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.32,1:23:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.49,1:23:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You forgot to touch my head.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.57,1:23:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.14,1:23:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,God blesses you now!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.52,1:23:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Indian culture, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.28,1:23:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.28,1:23:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I came all the way just to do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.18,1:23:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so important for me to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.84,1:23:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.14,1:23:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And last time I requested that you transmit no mind to me,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.32,1:23:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and you said it's been automatically done.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.60,1:23:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it already.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.52,1:23:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.50,1:23:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay a little farther away from that.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.38,1:23:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so close to the mic.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.62,1:23:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.12,1:23:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's better.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.76,1:23:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.66,1:24:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you already have that energy field.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.72,1:24:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.56,1:24:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.04,1:24:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's verify for her sake.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.16,1:24:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy field that you seek is already within your aura.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.76,1:24:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.18,1:24:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you got it last time.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.70,1:24:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you did that last time.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.28,1:24:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to know if there's any real progress that I've made.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.32,1:24:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.88,1:24:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of experiences I have where I just don't have any personal self,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.96,1:24:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, since the last year.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.06,1:24:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just feel like, who am I?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.50,1:24:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I kind of?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.64,1:24:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're looking for answers.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.62,1:24:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.08,1:24:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You have precipitated by your decision and by your will a certain process.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.62,1:24:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it's not up to you to question the process.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.62,1:24:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.07,1:24:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.93,1:24:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.43,1:24:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get stupid and fall flat on the ground, that's the way the process is going.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.85,1:24:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.63,1:24:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you go into a state of ecstasy, you have to put up with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.85,1:24:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way it's going.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.03,1:24:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.23,1:25:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And so sometimes, you know, I find it silly to use the personal word, personal I,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.35,1:25:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and because I know it's not real anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.36,1:25:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.84,1:25:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She knows this kind of word.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.56,1:25:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.14,1:25:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,After a while, you become, what happens is speaking more and more in the third person.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.09,1:25:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people complain that I write that way, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.64,1:25:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This happened, you know, and that happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.68,1:25:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a third person report.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.97,1:25:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The desire came up to ride the bicycle and then the skill arose.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.73,1:25:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't say the desire came up immediately.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.11,1:25:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,To ride the bicycle, the desire came up to learn how to ride a bicycle
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.99,1:25:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and out of that, the bicycling skill arose.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.77,1:25:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like happening of its own spontaneously.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.51,1:25:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to constantly put the pronoun in.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.16,1:25:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.82,1:25:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,As you eliminate narcissism, the pronoun disappears.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.08,1:25:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You see that phenomena are happening.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.10,1:26:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.82,1:26:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.77,1:26:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So sometimes, you know, it doesn't quite work when you're sitting in a dinner party or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.32,1:26:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're in what?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.62,1:26:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't work when you're in a dinner party.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.08,1:26:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.02,1:26:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So what to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.20,1:26:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see the body starts to eat and enjoy the food.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.74,1:26:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.57,1:26:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the body doing that.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.35,1:26:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.79,1:26:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.73,1:26:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Not your nose, not your ears.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.77,1:26:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.87,1:26:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The senses are seeking gratification.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.01,1:26:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So you witness the senses seeking gratification.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.55,1:26:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know that's part of your animal nature.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.13,1:26:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.43,1:26:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And without that, you would die.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.65,1:26:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't get hungry and eat, you die.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.44,1:26:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.88,1:26:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So the price of life is putting up with one's animal nature.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.88,1:26:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And you don't have to call it I.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.88,1:26:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.48,1:26:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can use, I can refrain from using the word I.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.98,1:26:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.60,1:26:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.06,1:26:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.70,1:26:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Even in a social gathering.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.26,1:27:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a certain skill.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.62,1:27:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.12,1:27:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.56,1:27:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.56,1:27:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming though, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.36,1:27:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.08,1:27:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,On its own.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.22,1:27:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.86,1:27:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.28,1:27:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,To be polite, you use certain pronouns.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.40,1:27:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.82,1:27:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.68,1:27:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.00,1:27:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.24,1:27:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't bring my level of consciousness down, will it?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.38,1:27:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.90,1:27:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.86,1:27:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you won't get dumber and dumber.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.70,1:27:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They have said I can only ask one question.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.80,1:27:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.94,1:27:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But may I ask one more?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.18,1:27:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.39,1:27:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If all the actions of the past, if all the actions of the past.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.72,1:27:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.28,1:27:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave an impression forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.28,1:27:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.00,1:27:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.18,1:27:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.05,1:27:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What role.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.11,1:27:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What role does atonement or the earning of good karma or the undoing of bad karma play?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.28,1:28:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how you evolve.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.96,1:28:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how you evolve.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.06,1:28:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you have a karmic debt, when you repay it, then your energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.80,1:28:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I always liken it to a magnetic field, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.00,1:28:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're like little iron filings.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.86,1:28:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And all, every decision you make affects the polarity.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.58,1:28:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,One end is negative, the other end is positive, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.54,1:28:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So every time you say yes, oh, I'll forgive them, he didn't know any better.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.68,1:28:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The iron filing moves a little more in the positive direction.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.94,1:28:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And you say, well, I hate him.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.74,1:28:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I just think he's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.44,1:28:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you move a little bit more in this direction.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.62,1:28:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So your little iron filing is like constantly moving in the field of gravitational field
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.34,1:28:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,of the infinite field of consciousness, which is infinitely powerful.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.14,1:28:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't need an arbitrary God who rewards.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.22,1:28:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You or gets mad at you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.24,1:28:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the automatic consequence of that which you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.64,1:29:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, the justice of God is absolute.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.70,1:29:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only be in an infinitely powerful magnetic field exactly where you should be.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.48,1:29:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So every time you forgive somebody, your magnetic polarity moves a little more this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.36,1:29:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You move a little more towards God.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.10,1:29:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So moving towards God is of your own inner consent.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.10,1:29:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So God doesn't force anybody to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.44,1:29:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So may I give you the example?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.82,1:29:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't very kind to my son when he was little.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.12,1:29:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.44,1:29:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And but I understand that now.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.78,1:29:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm being as loving as I possibly can be to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.90,1:29:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've explained it to him that, look, I didn't know what I was doing then.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.16,1:29:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.66,1:29:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.60,1:29:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So does that original action still have an effect forever?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.76,1:29:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all you can do.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.88,1:29:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.30,1:29:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So be it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.06,1:29:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.33,1:29:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I've addressed it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.51,1:29:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So you had a limitation at one time.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.17,1:29:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You realize this.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.87,1:29:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You had a limitation.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.79,1:30:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.55,1:30:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking so long.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.21,1:30:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know why you had that limitation either.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.58,1:30:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Good God.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.37,1:30:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you got a bus parked out in front there?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.15,1:30:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A bus?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.55,1:30:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Good God.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.17,1:30:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.93,1:30:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought something for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.35,1:30:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.15,1:30:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who looks just like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.19,1:30:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.04,1:30:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to save this, honey.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.46,1:30:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You put this right here, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.22,1:30:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.52,1:30:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.24,1:30:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.88,1:30:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, very pretty.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.28,1:30:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.86,1:30:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.28,1:30:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.74,1:30:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.88,1:30:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And you also.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.44,1:30:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.98,1:30:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.43,1:30:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All love is God's love.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.44,1:30:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.14,1:31:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.54,1:31:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No squeeze on the merchandise.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.04,1:31:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where they have that beautiful island they're building there, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.20,1:31:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.56,1:31:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're cute.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.19,1:31:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.63,1:31:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.12,1:31:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,People from places like Dubai, they go, oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.10,1:31:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A billion, billion dollar extension of the building of the country.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.16,1:31:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They go, uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.94,1:31:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're going to have the Queen Mary.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.36,1:31:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They go, uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.82,1:31:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, uh-huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.40,1:31:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Queen Mary, for God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.56,1:31:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Dubai is an interesting country.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.52,1:31:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you once again on behalf of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.78,1:31:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Your presence is truly a blessing to us all here.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.84,1:32:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My question for you is my experience thus far is that there's a depth and a breadth to consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.58,1:32:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,which you normally don't go into in the books.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.34,1:32:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But, for example, we have a relationship consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.92,1:32:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a space spiritual consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.72,1:32:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.83,1:32:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a professional consciousness, and that all these things play a part.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.71,1:32:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that something that you'd care to comment on or write about?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.11,1:32:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not different consciousnesses.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.61,1:32:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a consciousness of a certain level will express itself this way in this situation
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.79,1:32:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and this way in this situation.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.01,1:32:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A person with a different level of consciousness would express themselves differently in the
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.65,1:32:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,same situations.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.13,1:32:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So they're not different.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.71,1:32:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They're how that one person responds to all those things.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.40,1:32:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He sees them as opportunity or resents them.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.00,1:32:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,His obligations depends on how he sees it, or he sees it as a chance for camaraderie and good naturedness.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.21,1:32:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.97,1:32:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.45,1:33:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What's good for General Motors is good for the country.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.63,1:33:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.03,1:33:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we used to say when I grew up.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.74,1:33:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's good for General Motors is good for the country.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.84,1:33:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That was what we grew up with.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.23,1:33:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to quickly.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.75,1:33:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.87,1:33:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.27,1:33:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,When we pray to the Lord, does the Lord have to be a specific and an exclusive avatar?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.10,1:33:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so, because you know what you mean by it, and the Lord knows what you mean by it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.82,1:33:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,God's smart enough to know that he's Lord, and that you're trying to reach him.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.17,1:33:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that your intention already sets the level.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.87,1:33:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Your intention is already known.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.47,1:33:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.09,1:33:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.13,1:33:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.22,1:33:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Your intention is unmistakable.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.92,1:34:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.38,1:34:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.32,1:34:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to be with you again.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.76,1:34:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.09,1:34:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately, I'm crying.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.40,1:34:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And all the way up here, I've been reading the rest of this book, and part of the Yoga
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.20,1:34:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Vesastha, and Chorus of Miracles, and it seems like the thing for me to do next is to stop
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.68,1:34:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,thinking.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.83,1:34:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.71,1:34:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's illegal in certain parts of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.98,1:34:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But the first fear that comes up is that, Neil, you're not ready to do that yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.22,1:34:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,To give up thinking?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.18,1:34:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.48,1:34:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.44,1:34:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't want to, you know, get impatient and then come to a place where I've failed.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.32,1:34:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get a chance to give up thinking, by all means, take it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.64,1:34:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.06,1:35:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can't get ahead of myself then.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.14,1:35:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get a chance to give up thinking, do so.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.59,1:35:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.53,1:35:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything from that point on is autonomous.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.37,1:35:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to think about what to say to you, do I?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.01,1:35:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.47,1:35:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes right up.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.25,1:35:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to think about being here.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.39,1:35:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to think about that thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.15,1:35:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.55,1:35:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.91,1:35:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Join me.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.98,1:35:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up thinking.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.10,1:35:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.82,1:35:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.38,1:35:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.82,1:35:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.95,1:35:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A bad habit.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.20,1:35:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.71,1:35:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been on the path for a lot of years, and I've had a lot of growth.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.89,1:35:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the past year, I think it's really been coming apart at the seams.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.27,1:35:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've really found that a lot of it has been, like, self-serving.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.77,1:35:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've been, like, throwing myself into the path to avoid dealing with issues and,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.03,1:35:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, with spiritual courage and integrity.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.59,1:35:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.95,1:36:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.41,1:36:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And now they've really come up to be dealt with, and they're not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.05,1:36:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And, like, as I've been facing this, it's like, wow, I'm just, like, a really broken person.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.62,1:36:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.54,1:36:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a mess.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.68,1:36:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.12,1:36:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I just feel like...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:15.28,1:36:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a mess.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.20,1:36:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.70,1:36:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.22,1:36:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And I feel like I failed you as a student.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.84,1:36:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.40,1:36:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And I feel like...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.54,1:36:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, seriously, though, like...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.36,1:36:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You come and made a mess out of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.68,1:36:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.16,1:36:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.34,1:36:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And I feel like, even though I see it, it's like,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.02,1:36:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,there's just a weakness in my own will to, like, get through it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.76,1:36:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're expecting some kind of linear discipline progression of things.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.66,1:36:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't happen that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.16,1:36:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You go from chaos to collapse to failure to jubilation and then discouragement and then...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.68,1:36:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there's no way you can rate whether you're making progress or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.81,1:36:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.49,1:36:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.17,1:36:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,When you finally make real progress,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.57,1:37:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the question doesn't even...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.11,1:37:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The question doesn't even arise whether you're making progress.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.85,1:37:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.56,1:37:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,See, it's your intention and your alignment,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.86,1:37:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and the rest is not up to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.04,1:37:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think that's part that really worries me,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.32,1:37:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is, like, what are my intentions?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.64,1:37:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of it seems so self-serving a lot of the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.72,1:37:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-serving like what?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.28,1:37:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Worshiping worldly success, material success,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.70,1:37:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,position in the world, special...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.10,1:37:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, those are all things you acknowledge is going on within yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.76,1:37:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And you say that's normal for a certain age.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.42,1:37:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And each of those things, maybe you'll have to live it through a bit to decide.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.27,1:37:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing wrong with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.49,1:37:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing wrong with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.03,1:37:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I think in the Bible it says,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.25,1:37:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,don't want worldly success.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.53,1:37:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.43,1:37:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Just that a rich man can't get through the eye of the needle, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.52,1:38:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a shortage of poverty.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.09,1:38:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.33,1:38:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He's suffering from a poverty shortage.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.34,1:38:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.00,1:38:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.04,1:38:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.24,1:38:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,See, if you weren't okay, you would.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.62,1:38:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't be worrying about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.46,1:38:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.34,1:38:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.62,1:38:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.28,1:38:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Susan Hurd.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.08,1:38:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.86,1:38:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come from Dublin to see you, so I'm very pleased to be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.72,1:38:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dublin, Ireland.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.76,1:38:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.70,1:38:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought it was in Iowa, not in Iowa.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.27,1:38:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She thought Dublin was in Iowa.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.39,1:38:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,In Iowa.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.24,1:38:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.14,1:38:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, it has changed.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.20,1:38:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It has changed as I was standing up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.70,1:39:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You calibrated homeopathy in truth versus falsehood as 200 and over the years, I'm a medical physician
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.28,1:39:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,as well, and over the years I've had a lot of contact with homeopaths who have had miraculous
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.66,1:39:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,results with homeopathy where I know that ordinary medicine wouldn't have been able
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.54,1:39:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,to affect.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.54,1:39:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.54,1:39:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.60,1:39:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wondering, how come it calibrates at 200?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.20,1:39:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.20,1:39:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.20,1:39:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't calibrate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.20,1:39:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I didn't calibrate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.20,1:39:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Homeopathy?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.20,1:39:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't make it be that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.20,1:39:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably talking about the scientific theory of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.20,1:39:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you calibrated?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.72,1:39:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This week's newspapers are full of deaths by homeopaths doing liposuction, five or six
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.32,1:39:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,of them losing their licenses from not knowing what they can do and what they can't do.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.22,1:39:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you talk about public image in this week's Arizona Republic, it's not so great.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.95,1:39:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What aspect of homeopathy did you calibrate?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.11,1:39:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I just talked about homeopathy.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.99,1:39:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Homeopathy as a theory, you see, as a...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.75,1:40:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Any practice in certain practitioner's hands is excellent.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.49,1:40:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.49,1:40:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The same practice in an idiot's hands is, you know, terrible, so homeopathy as a field
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.45,1:40:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,of science.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.45,1:40:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Homeopathy as a field of science doesn't measure up rationally.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.02,1:40:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The effects of it, though, are...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.18,1:40:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking about two different things.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.30,1:40:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.30,1:40:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to do homeopathy.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.30,1:40:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.37,1:40:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.37,1:40:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,205.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.37,1:40:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's at 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.07,1:40:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Homeopathy is 200, so that means the result is more likely intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.07,1:40:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.07,1:40:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The intention of the patient, the intention of the doctor is probably going to bring about.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.52,1:40:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That has to do with the law of similars, does it not?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.90,1:40:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.90,1:40:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.90,1:40:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's do the law of similars.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.90,1:40:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The law of similars calibrates over 200, is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.76,1:40:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,205.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.82,1:40:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,210.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.82,1:40:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,205.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.37,1:40:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the law of similars is about 205.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.57,1:40:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.57,1:40:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask me why.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.37,1:40:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I understand that.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.37,1:40:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any money in the market, do I?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.37,1:40:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, I understand that.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.37,1:41:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any position about homeopathy.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.37,1:41:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I understand that.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.37,1:41:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.37,1:41:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.37,1:41:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm suffering from an incurable disease, I want to see everybody, including every
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.50,1:41:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,homeopath in town.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.50,1:41:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.50,1:41:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.50,1:41:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Western medicine, like, calibrates at 450, 460.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.50,1:41:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.50,1:41:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Western medicine.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.50,1:41:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,460, whatever it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.50,1:41:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.50,1:41:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,440.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.50,1:41:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,440.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.50,1:41:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,440.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.87,1:41:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Academic medicine.
