Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.21,1:47:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's ways, you know, you can test kinesiology yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:46.21,1:47:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you can say, you know, there's a closed ring finger, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:52.40,1:47:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The other way is to just hold a bunch of heavy dictionaries and say, my consciousness level
Dialogue: 0,1:47:57.38,1:47:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,is over 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.38,1:48:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it is, you'll see the weight, the books weigh something.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.70,1:48:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My consciousness level is over 300.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.88,1:48:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.88,1:48:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My consciousness level is over 800.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.38,1:48:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The simplest way is you'll notice that your strength, your strength fluctuates.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:19.12,1:48:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So with a little practice, you can do it all by yourself, just lifting books.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:22.42,1:48:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.00,1:48:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.00,1:48:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's just so you'll know that, because your level of...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:28.00,1:48:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.00,1:48:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.00,1:48:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.42,1:48:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.40,1:48:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Enthusiasm.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.40,1:48:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.78,1:48:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,400 is more hard.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.77,1:48:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,400 is reading a book.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:40.77,1:48:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The 300 is being a volunteer fireman.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:41.77,1:48:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:42.77,1:48:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So you just sort of sense where you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.78,1:48:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.78,1:48:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.78,1:48:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You just sort of sense it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.42,1:48:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You just keep going straight ahead no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:55.99,1:49:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:00.83,1:49:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.83,1:49:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.18,1:49:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:05.18,1:49:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you found in a love relationship between a man and a woman that there needs to be
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.00,1:49:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,some range of...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.18,1:49:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness level for it to be enduring?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.18,1:49:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't noticed that.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.18,1:49:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.18,1:49:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,People who are quite the spirit can get along with each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:20.18,1:49:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at Socrates and his wife, Zantippe.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:23.85,1:49:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.85,1:49:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So it could be a wide range, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:28.17,1:49:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.17,1:49:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.17,1:49:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.17,1:49:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Most couples will accommodate to each other and balance it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.80,1:49:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's too far out of line, that relationship won't last, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:46.80,1:49:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't last.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:47.80,1:49:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.11,1:49:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:51.53,1:49:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you learn from each other either way, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:55.07,1:49:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She's back.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.94,1:50:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's going to cost you a dollar now.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:01.98,1:50:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Flippo.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:03.27,1:50:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:04.27,1:50:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, George.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.46,1:50:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all done.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.46,1:50:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:08.65,1:50:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You got to run faster.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.65,1:50:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too slow.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:10.65,1:50:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you guys so slow over there?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:11.65,1:50:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:12.68,1:50:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.68,1:50:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to sit in front of you and tell you thank you and I love you and God bless
Dialogue: 0,1:50:18.68,1:50:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you for everything you've done for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.68,1:50:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.68,1:50:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:21.68,1:50:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You've transformed my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:22.68,1:50:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:23.68,1:50:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your love.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.68,1:50:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:25.68,1:50:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:27.93,1:50:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.93,1:50:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.93,1:50:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.93,1:50:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.93,1:50:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.93,1:50:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:33.93,1:50:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:34.93,1:50:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.90,1:50:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.90,1:50:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We're saving dessert for the end here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:41.90,1:50:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:43.48,1:50:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.48,1:50:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.48,1:50:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for your lecture.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.48,1:50:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.48,1:50:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What I got was when you dealt with your demons, that moment of despair, what you got was
Dialogue: 0,1:50:53.48,1:50:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the way out was to verify the sanctity of your own life.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:56.48,1:50:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I get that right?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.12,1:50:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And how do you ...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:59.12,1:51:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no, that came as a greater understanding later on.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.12,1:51:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're referring to now.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:11.17,1:51:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, how do you recommend verifying the sanctity of your own life?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:16.90,1:51:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's a good way to get that?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:17.90,1:51:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Verify it?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:18.90,1:51:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:19.90,1:51:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to verify it.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:20.90,1:51:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just take my word for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.90,1:51:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing exists without except by divine ordinance.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:25.90,1:51:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing exists without divine ordinance.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.51,1:51:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Consequently, you exist only as a consequence of divine ordinance.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:34.51,1:51:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:36.57,1:51:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you're capable of spontaneous combustion or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.39,1:51:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.39,1:51:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All that exists does so by virtue of divine grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:49.74,1:51:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Divine grace, which is called divine ordinance.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:52.74,1:51:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:09.34,1:52:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I hug everyone in this room.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:11.34,1:52:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And I give thanks to almighty God for the gift of all of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:16.34,1:52:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't forget that we are all one.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:18.34,1:52:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That we come into this world together, you know, over a couple decades.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:23.47,1:52:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,In my time dimension, that's the same time.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:26.47,1:52:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Over 50 years or so, it's the same time.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.47,1:52:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We all come in together.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:32.47,1:52:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And we all leave together.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:34.47,1:52:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And we all do this as a unison.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:36.47,1:52:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We all do this as a unison.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:38.47,1:52:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:39.47,1:52:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And the fear of death is the fear of death.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:40.47,1:52:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And the fear of death is really not, is the fear of separation.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.66,1:52:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you about this during World War II.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:47.66,1:52:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And this mine was going to go off.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.66,1:52:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And he said, what if it goes off?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:51.66,1:52:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll die.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.66,1:52:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said, well, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.66,1:52:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, what will happen if it explodes?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:56.66,1:52:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said, well, we'll die.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:58.66,1:53:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And he looked at me and said, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:00.66,1:53:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he got.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.08,1:53:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We wouldn't die alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:04.08,1:53:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We will die together.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.11,1:53:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So look at the, I want you to get rid of the fear of death.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:09.11,1:53:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a fear of dying.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.11,1:53:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fear of being alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:12.11,1:53:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, being committed to a group like this is not possible to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:16.11,1:53:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:18.11,1:53:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:19.11,1:53:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So none of us are ever going to be separated.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:22.11,1:53:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a fear of death.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.11,1:53:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fear of separation.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.11,1:53:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:26.11,1:53:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:27.11,1:53:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway, God bless you all.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:29.11,1:53:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And I give thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:31.11,1:53:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You are God's gift to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:33.11,1:53:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:47.55,1:53:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And the world's lucky that we're here, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:49.55,1:53:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,When we give them the bill.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:55.63,1:53:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Saving the bill, the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:57.76,1:53:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,100 trillion trillion dollars.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:59.76,1:54:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:00.76,1:54:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm submitting a bill.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:02.89,1:54:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
